{"tid":959384,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"俾人誤會係跟蹤狂","createTime":"2018-12-28T13:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T14:11:15.000Z","uid":86308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d300e36cc63b840f8e97f2b249934973512a944f","tid":959384,"uid":86308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T13:55:39.000Z","msg":"話說今日收工坐完地鐵返屋企<br />\n跟住行返去途中<br />\n見到一個住同一棟大廈嘅女仔<br />\n咁咪繼續一齊行囉<br />\n反正大家都係返去同一個地方<br />\n行行吓見到佢突然加速腳步<br />\n之後我照平時步速咁行<br />\n跟住到等lift 嗰陣<br />\n一打開lift 門又見到佢<br />\n成個氣氛好尷尬<br />\n搞到我好似變態佬咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae56c0f42ebe9926bc193f8c2c9b3aedd5db4f85","tid":959384,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T13:56:57.000Z","msg":"樓主嗰樣應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a47b6a5f3c05610419d2437eed78164f6b17ad4","tid":959384,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T13:59:21.000Z","msg":"好心樓主唔好咁變態啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a54b2bec1407f98cef207a5a7bd0ba33533663d9","tid":959384,"uid":199902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:03:38.000Z","msg":"原來你就係個變態佬<br />\n人又矮 又成個八両金咁樣衰<br />\n又對住我搲J淫笑<br />\n入咗lift仲要係咁一路喘氣 一路chok自己條J<br />\n我冇報警都算益咗你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98a4449c3030ec730f5321d69eac413c1882b71","tid":959384,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T14:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AwAwoSP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAwAwoSP.jpg&h=0c45b5e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7edbf1a5d3a1f0109a3c812d907712f320995b07","tid":959384,"uid":100442,"